decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a fast and aggressive Elf tribe strategy. The deck utilizes various Elf creatures and mana-producing cards to quickly summon a large board presence. Cards like Collected Company and Chord of Calling allow for efficient creature tutoring and instant speed responses. The deck also includes cards like Shaman of the Pack and Dwynen's Elite to deal direct damage and generate additional Elf tokens. The land base is optimized for mana production and consistency, ensuring a fast and consistent Elf onslaught.
